@Kirandeep_Chahal walked the @Dior Pre-Fall 2023 show in Mumbai and she also took us on a tour of some of the city’s must-dos. From a morning Chai in the streets to the adrenaline right before walking the runway under the Gateway of India, and the happiness backstage with @Maria Grazia Chiuri: it was a true journey!

On the cover of @moreorlessmag 🥦
Material World | Issue 07 | Out now!

Every scrap of fabric tells a thousand yarns; offcuts, though, are often left to gather dust. To bring these end-of-roll pieces to life, we sourced deadstock textiles from designers across the world, draping them on the body in couture-inspired silhouettes and offsetting them with recycled jewellery. Kirandeep is wearing deadstock material from @stellamccartney.
